# Test Fixtures for Kaido AI Shell

This directory contains test data and mock models for the Kaido AI Shell test suite.

## Files

- `sample_commands.txt` - Sample commands for testing command execution
- `test_config.toml` - Test configuration file
- `mock_responses.json` - Mock AI responses for testing
- `test_models/` - Directory for test model files (if needed)

## Usage

These fixtures are used by the test suite to provide consistent test data across different test scenarios.
